title: Sex and the City AUDIO For PFD Release CD2 (Not By PFD)
description:
This is a ripped audio for CD2 Of the PFD release which had no audio on the CD2 File. its taken from NYSLVR Cam release and has been through a few filters to try and improve the quality. 

Use virtual dub to add to CD2 stream and save as direct stream copy

Any probs post a comment

Is in sync all way through up to 58 mins when it slips for 9 sec slightly then gets back in, it was hard work but its all i could do and hope it helps those who want to watch it..
